title: 820-00165 board not power on with original adapter.
message: 820-00165 board not power with original adapter. but working fine with battery and copy adapter.

title: 820-00165 board not power on with original adapter.
message:
Looks like leakage on power input stage.
Usually Q7180, sometimes R/D7012.
Post R7180/81 and R7185/86 values (ohm scale), measured onboard.
